%% E216 - Agentic loop sequence - F1-17 Chat Tools
%% Source: docs/design/f1-17-chat-tools-architecture.md (E215)
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Controller as ChatController
    participant Handler as ChatQueryHandler
    participant Registry as IToolRegistry
    participant Agent as IAgentChatService
    participant LLM as GPT-4o
    participant Tool as Tool Handler

    Client->>Controller: POST /api/chat (query)
    Controller->>Handler: CreateStream(ChatQueryCommand)

    Note over Handler: Build messages: system prompt + user query

    Handler->>Registry: GetToolDefinitions()
    Registry-->>Handler: tool definitions (8 tools)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Handler,LLM: Agentic Loop (max 5 iterations)

        Handler->>Agent: StreamWithToolsAsync(messages, tools, options)
        Agent->>LLM: CompleteChatStreamingAsync(messages + tools)

        alt Model returns text (FinishReason: Stop)
            loop SSE text stream
                LLM-->>Agent: TextChunkEvent
                Agent-->>Handler: TextChunkEvent
                Handler-->>Controller: data: text chunk
                Controller-->>Client: data: text chunk
            end
            LLM-->>Agent: DoneEvent(Stop)
            Agent-->>Handler: DoneEvent(Stop)
            Handler-->>Controller: data: [DONE]
            Controller-->>Client: data: [DONE]

        else Model returns tool_calls (FinishReason: ToolCalls)
            LLM-->>Agent: ToolCallRequestEvent(s)
            Agent-->>Handler: ToolCallRequestEvent(s)

            loop For each tool call
                Handler-->>Controller: event: tool_start
                Controller-->>Client: event: tool_start

                Handler->>Registry: ExecuteAsync(toolName, argsJson, context)
                Registry->>Tool: ExecuteAsync(argsJson, context)
                Tool-->>Registry: result string
                Registry-->>Handler: result string

                Handler-->>Controller: event: tool_end
                Controller-->>Client: event: tool_end
            end

            Note over Handler: Append assistant message + tool results to messages
            Note over Handler: Increment iteration, re-invoke if under max
        end
    end
